This update to the code makes it much nicer to read and enhance if we want to add more features, thank you.

---

If you are up for a fast follower PR, it may be nice to do an update for the view.

- `wagtail/contrib/styleguide/views.py` - we need to add `header_icon = "image"` to the view
- We can then 'flatten' the view to avoid using the shared header template
- We can move the 'sticky' minimap into the header block

Something like this... (note, formatting will need to be run to update the nesting).

```html
{% extends "wagtailadmin/generic/base.html" %}
{% load wagtailadmin_tags i18n %}

{% block extra_css %}
    {{ block.super }}

    {{ example_form.media.css }}
{% endblock %}

{% block bodyclass %}styleguide{% endblock %}

{% block header %}
    <div class="w-sticky w-top-0 w-z-header">
        <aside aria-label="{% trans 'Minimap' %}" data-minimap-container></aside>
    </div>
    {{ block.super }}
{% endblock %}

{% block main_content %}

    {% comment %} REMOVE header & <div class="nice-padding"> & then keep the rest of the original stuff inside... {% endcomment %}
        {% panel id="typography" heading="Typography" %}
            <h1>This is an h1</h1>
```
